
compile options
 - language aware!!
link options
run options
run arguments
tags: -> comp + link + run opt
test target
  - type
    - text
	- number
	- array
	- binary
  - values / blob / verbatim

---

target is:
 1) manifest
 2) single directory, if it has Makefile
 3) each file (with known ending)

option to allow one to use only manifest?

---

1. construct list of targets
2. loop over targets
  2.1. compile target (if Makefile, use make)
  2.2. run target
  2.3. check output
3. print stats

